Additionally, it is very unclear how to operate the lists and the other app settings without the tutorial showing the instructions. I nearly had to go back to the instructions just to find out how to upload the photos on Day 2. Overall, a very poorly made app with little functionality to the average user that is not using it for a psychology study.
